ing: 1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "No bake easy cheesecake-- won't last long!  You can spoon any flavor pie filling over top of cheesecake  if desired."
ins: In a large bowl beat together the cream cheese and sugar until smooth. Gently fold in the whipped topping. Spoon into the prepared crust. Refrigerate 3 hours, or until set.
